31a8bd2e1582d12bb6b237fd","tid":2418080,"uid":16981,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a789d1ec4ed420a53d37f6356d54210caf8dd801","tid":2418080,"uid":352218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T11:50:59.000Z","msg":"6年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T01:28:59.000Z","msg":"佢冇拍拖？<br />\n6年時間算好長<br />\n如果佢第一年都唔鍾意<br />\n第二、三、四、五、六都唔鍾意<br />\n你覺得第七、八、九、十年會？<br />\n佢青春到幾多個十年？<br />\n你唔介意，佢都要結婚有自己家庭<br />\n我知你好想同佢一齊<br />\n我真係明我真係知<br />\n我啱啱被分手，我都好撚想復合<br />\n但有時唔愛就唔愛，唔想一齊就唔想<br />\n冇得迫，起碼你哋仲係好朋友<br />\n拍拖離離合合，但朋友係一世<br />\n雖然你俾我揀都會想再一齊<br />\n但重點係就係冇得俾我哋揀<br />\n唉，祝你好運啦"},{"pid":"e1e8c4887a1a249bb5a3575a82df1f262084a0f2","tid":2418080,"uid":173973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8c2c9b05d2113f50b39074662e7cae1753072481","tid":2418080,"uid":268410,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"af74afc7993fb6eb12e84f712531dc90a57729a9","tid":2418080,"uid":249721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96d74ef3d5374414b53c8462f9ae8e03c485451f","tid":2418080,"uid":268410,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:17:26.000Z","msg":"公司同事 追左十年 由中學開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後追到手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:18:22.000Z","msg":"你中間有冇拍拖"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T13:26:58.000Z","msg":"唔係我 係我同事老公追咗佢十年 佢老公婚禮到喊住講 追左佢十年終於娶到佢先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中間個同事有拍兩三次拖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T01:40:26.000Z","msg":"咁條女係是但搵個人埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}